# SAFE-LD

This repository contains the scripts used to run simulations and experiments for **SAFE-LD**.

## Repository Structure

- `fine_mapping_functions/`  
  Contains the functions used to perform fine-mapping using both SAFE-LD and SAFE-LDss.

- `ld_creation_functions/`  
  Contains the functions used to create SAFE-LD and SAFE-LDss during experiments.

- `SAFE-LDss.R`  
  Main function that can be used by anyone to create SAFE-LD from summary statistics.
